code: @Override protected void testProgram() throws Exception {     ExecutionEnvironment env = ExecutionEnvironment.getExecutionEnvironment().     DataSet<Long> inputStatic = env.generateSequence(1, 4).     DataSet<Long> inputIteration = env.generateSequence(1, 4).     IterativeDataSet<Long> iteration = inputIteration.iterate(3).     DataSet<Long> result = iteration.closeWith(inputStatic.union(inputStatic).union(iteration.union(iteration))).     result.output(new LocalCollectionOutputFormat<Long>(this.result)).     env.execute(). }
@Override protected void postSubmit() throws Exception {     assertEquals(88, result.size()). }
